OL,6,FSpeaking at a press conference on
OL,7,FMonday afternoon in Washington, Mr
OL,8,FTrump said: "In a little while, you'll
OL,9,Fbe seeing I'm suing the BBC for
OL,10,Fputting words in my mouth literally.
OL,11,FThey had me saying things that I never
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"We'll be filing that suit probably
OL,15,Fthis afternoon or tomorrow morning."
