OL,3,CTrump says he will file lawsuit
OL,4,Cagainst BBC imminently
OL,6,FAfter the memo, which was written by
OL,7,FMichael Prescott, a former external
OL,8,Fadviser to the BBC's editorial
OL,9,Fstandards committee, was leaked, BBC
OL,10,Fchairman Samir Shah apologised on
OL,11,Fbehalf of the BBC over an "error of
OL,12,Fjudgment" and accepted the editing of
OL,13,Fthe 2024 documentary gave "the
OL,14,Fimpression of a direct call for
OL,15,Fviolent action".
OL,17,FThe programme was broadcast a week
OL,18,Fbefore the US election in November
OL,19,F2024.
