OL,3,CTrump says he will file lawsuit
OL,4,Cagainst BBC imminently
OL,6,FMr Trump has a history of suing news
OL,7,Forganisations in the US and is
OL,8,Fcurrently engaged in legal action with
OL,9,Fthe New York Times and the Wall Street
OL,10,FJournal, with mixed results.
OL,12,FHe settled a case against ABC in 2024
OL,13,Ffor $15m (#11m) but most of his
OL,14,Flawsuits end up getting dismissed by
OL,15,Fjudges.
OL,17,FBBC News reported that the broadcaster
OL,18,Fhad set out five main arguments in a
OL,19,Fletter to Mr Trump's legal team as to
OL,20,Fwhy it did not believe there was a
OL,21,Fbasis for a defamation claim.
